## 4. OpenSpec Workflow

```
1. Create: openspec new change <name>
2. Validate: openspec validate <change-id> --strict
3. Implement: follow tasks.md phase order
4. Validate: openspec validate <change-id> --all
5. Archive: openspec archive <change-id>
```

## 5. Validation Levels

| Scope | OpenSpec | Tests | Quality Gate |
|---|---|---|---|
| Docs only | Not required | Not required | Not required |
| Single change | `--strict` | Module-level | Not required |
| Core pipeline | `--all` | Full | Required |
| Pre-push/archive | `--all` | Full | Required (0 skip) |

